Name: SSL / TLS Versions Supported
Description: This plugin detects which SSL and TLS versions are supported by the remote service.
Solution: Enable support for TLS 1.2 and/or 1.3, and disable support for TLS 1.0 and 1.1.

Name: Spectre Attack Vulnerability
Description: A vulnerability exists in the processor that could allow an attacker to read sensitive information.

Name: SMBv3 RCE 'Wormable' Vulnerability
Description: A remote code execution vulnerability exists in Microsoft Server Message Block 3.1.1 (SMBv3).

Name: Microsoft SQL Server Unsupported Version
Description: The remote Microsoft SQL Server is an unsupported version.
Solution: Upgrade to a supported version of Microsoft SQL Server.
